Package com.tractrac.subscription.lib.impl.io

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    DataControllerAsio.Listener
    Provides information on the status of live and stored data.
    DataControllerAsio.TimeListener
    A callback that will be called when the UTC time of the live data server is received.
    ILatestDataReceiver
    Used for providing the user of LatestDataController with live and stored data.
    IOnlineDataReceiver
    Used for providing the user of OnlineDataController with live data.
    ISequenceDataReceiver
    Used for providing the user of SequenceDataController with live and stored data.
    IStoredDataProgress
    Used for receiving information about stored data fetching, including a progress indicator.
    IUserMessage
    Interface for sending a user message
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DataControllerAsio
    Mostly a convenience wrapper for TypeControllerCollection, but is tied to a specific Asio I/O service.
    LatestDataController
    A TypeController for latest data
    OnlineDataController
    A TypeController for online data.
    SequenceDataController
    A TypeController for sequence data.
    TypeController
    A TypeController is tied to a specific TypeDescriptor and works independently from all other TypeControllers.
    TypeControllerCollection
    This class has list of TypeControllers, for which it can start and stop live and stored data retreival.
    UserMessageThread
    Helper class, executed by a separate thread, where all messages added to the class is send on by the separate thread.
